PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FThe ex-businesswoman, who enjoyed a
OL,8,F"successful career" as a sales
OL,9,Fdirector for a global firm, started
OL,10,Fvoluntary work in 2017 as a member of
OL,11,Fan Independent Monitoring Board (IMB)
OL,12,Fwhich scrutinises conditions for
OL,13,Fprisoners and monitors how they are
OL,14,Ftreated.
OL,16,FShe was later appointed chairwoman of
OL,17,FHMP Liverpool's IMB in January 2021.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
