FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FA search of her home address following
OL,8,Fher arrest in August 2021 revealed she
OL,9,Fhad two custom-made pillows with
OL,10,FWestall's face embossed on them, which
OL,11,Falso sported a gun, Liverpool Crown
OL,12,FCourt heard.
OL,14,FWestall was jailed for life with a
OL,15,Fminimum term of 22 years in 2019 for
OL,16,Fthe manslaughter of James Meadows, 17,
OL,17,Fwho was shot in the head while on a
OL,18,Fmotorbike in Huyton, Merseyside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
