FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FDuring the search of Spree's home, it
OL,8,Fwas also noted by officers she had a
OL,9,Ftattoo on her chest of a bumblebee
OL,10,Fholding a love heart, with the word
OL,11,F"Masterpiece" underneath.
OL,13,FSpree explained it was a nickname her
OL,14,Ffriend called her but the tattoo later
OL,15,Fmatched images and descriptions found
OL,16,Fin messages exchanged between her and
OL,17,FWestall.
OL,19,FA thank you card from Westall was also
OL,20,Fdiscovered which read: "You Master
OL,21,FPiece. Hugs and Kisses, Dylan xxxxx."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@MO]|D@XOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
