PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FMother-of-two Spree also sexted two
OL,8,Fother inmates at HMP Liverpool over a
OL,9,F20-month period which led to her
OL,10,Fbringing in the Class B drug, along
OL,11,Fwith mobile phones, Sim cards and
OL,12,Fphone chargers.
OL,14,FDetails of the requests from Westall,
OL,15,FThomas Porterfield, 44, and a third
OL,16,Finmate, who cannot be named for legal
OL,17,Freasons, were found in messages on her
OL,18,Fphone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
