PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FA police investigation was launched
OL,8,Ffollowing numerous prison intelligence
OL,9,Freports outlining concerns over
OL,10,FSpree's interactions with the three
OL,11,Fprisoners.
OL,13,FProsecutor Andrew Scott said: "So
OL,14,Ffrequent were the deliveries that Ms
OL,15,FSpree described herself as the
OL,16,Fprisoners' version of Deliveroo."
OL,26,@uD@_OUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
