PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FSpree, of Hale Bank Avenue, Huyton,
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,9,Fto misconduct in a public office,
OL,10,Fconspiracy to supply cannabis and
OL,11,Fconspiracy to convey prohibited items
OL,12,Finto prison.
OL,14,FShe was jailed for five years and
OL,15,Fthree months.
OL,17,FWestall and Porterfield, of Greenwich
OL,18,FAvenue, Widnes, also pleaded guilty at
OL,19,Fearlier hearings to conspiracy to
OL,20,Fsupply cannabis and convey prohibited
OL,21,Fitems into prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
