FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FWestall received a 12-month sentence
OL,8,Fwhich he will serve in addition to his
OL,9,Fminimum life term, while Porterfield
OL,10,Freceived 22 months in custody,
OL,11,Fsuspended for 18 months.
OL,13,FThe third inmate was jailed for two
OL,14,Fyears and 10 months after he admitted
OL,15,Fconspiracy to convey prohibited items,
OL,16,Fincluding cannabis, into prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
