PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780510264
OL,3,CCorrupt prison watchdog boss jailed
OL,4,Cfor smuggling cannabis to convicted
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FWestall's brother Michael Westall, 28,
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to 20 months in custody,
OL,9,Fsuspended for 18 months, after he
OL,10,Fadmitted conspiracy to supply cannabis
OL,11,Fand convey prohibited items into
OL,12,Fprison.
OL,14,FHe became part of the smuggling
OL,15,Foperation when Dylan Westall
OL,16,Fintroduced him to Spree, with evidence
OL,17,Fof the pair meeting up at Spree's home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
